-- BP's Hayward: Gulf oil spill was preventable
-- 
-- Thu Jun 17, 2010 3:32pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/06/17/us-oil-spill-prevent-idUSTRE65G5J820100617

 

 WASHINGTON  (Reuters) - BP Plc Chief Executive Tony Hayward said on Thursday the oil spill in the Gulf of Mexico was preventable. 

 "I believe that all accidents are preventable," Hayward told a House Energy and Commerce Subcommittee on Oversight and Investigations in response to a question from a lawmaker.